thongtin: You will be taken on a trip by your lover, and the two of you will have fun days together.
You will be taken by your partner to meet their family, to ask for permission to marry you.
You will be given gifts by your lover, not on the occasion of a holiday at all
He will give you a Rolls-Royce car as a birthday present.
You will receive a surprise gift from your significant other. Your family will have a new baby.
Three years later, you two will be able to buy a villa.
In 3 years, you will become a billionaire.
After 1 year of being in a relationship, you will be fattened up by your significant other by 10 kg.
At the age of 30, the husband will take his family on a world tour using his own airplane.
At 37 years old, the husband and wife both became a nationally famous acting couple.
After discovering her husband's affair with his ex-girlfriend, the wife went to the ex-girlfriend's house to confront her and even resorted to cutting her hair and physically assaulting her.
After getting married, the husband and wife inherited a large amount of assets from the husband's stepfather.
At the age of 60, they were happy to have their 3 children all grown up and successful.
His greatest joy is waking up every morning to see his ugly wife preparing breakfast.
tomLuocText: Morning Bliss with His Beloved Wife

thongtin: The girl was surprised when she received a proposal from her boyfriend in a crowded place
tomLuocText: A Surprise Proposal in the Crowd

thongtin: The girl feels that she is very lucky to have an ugly husband, not afraid that her husband will go with her.
After 2 years of love, they decided to go home together.
tomLuocText: Two Years of Love, One Journey Home

thongtin: You will feel happy when traveling with the person you love together.
Every day after work, the girl is picked up by her boyfriend.
In the middle of the night, the girl's phone suddenly rang, it turned out that her boyfriend called to wish her good night.
The young man was at work, learned that he had won the lottery, and had to stop working to receive the prize.
The girl was given a watch by her boyfriend on her 20th birthday.
tomLuocText: The Gift of Time: 20th Birthday Watch

thongtin: The girl was surprised to see another girl besides her lover, she was very happy because she had a reason to break up with this boyfriend, to start a relationship with someone else.
tomLuocText: The Gift of Clarity: Love's Crossroads

thongtin: The girl who was abandoned by her ex-boyfriend for a very bad reason, accidentally saw that the beauty of her current ex-girlfriend was even worse than her.
The girl wearing a new dress entered the company and everyone complimented her that she was prettier than yesterday.
tomLuocText: A New Dress, a New Radiance
